title: Specialist Industrial Cables for Naval Applications
text:
Print Email Company Details 
SAB Brockskes offers heat-resistant cables for the naval industry. 
The range of cables includes halogen-free, silicone, cable track and ethernet, along with a broad variety of specialised ones. 
Please download the free brochure for detailed information of SAB's naval cables products. Available Downloads
